<div
  class=" bg-slate-500 bg-[url(/un2.jpg)] bg-top bg-blend-multiply min-h-[70vh] bg-cover  p-8 md:px-40 md:py-20 mt-20 py-20 justify-center grid grid-cols-2 gap-5 items-center">
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-0">
      <h1 class="text-6xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Transforming the Future of Work Together</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-white mb-8">
        At Skyfusion, we're on a mission to redefine how people and companies collaborate, innovate, and succeed. Our vision is a world where education, technology, and creativity merge seamlessly to create smarter, more sustainable, and fulfilling ways of working.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-semibold mb-4 text-white">Empowering Innovation and Growth</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-white mb-8">
        We believe the conventional approach to work needs a revolution. Imagine a future where ingenuity thrives, knowledge is shared freely, and everyone is inspired to reach their full potential. At Skyfusion, we are dedicated to making this vision a reality by connecting minds and fostering an environment where brilliance meets opportunity.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4 text-white">Building a Better Tomorrow</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-white mb-8">
        Our goal is simple yet profound: to create a platform that breaks down barriers and unites brilliant individuals and forward-thinking companies. No matter where you are or what challenges you face, Skyfusion is here to help you collaborate, learn, and build incredible things together.
      </p>
      
   <div class="my-10">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-white">Join Us in Shaping the Future</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-white">
      Together, we can inspire change, drive progress, and create a brighter future for all. Let's illuminate what's possible and turn dreams into reality, one innovative step at a time.
    </p>
   </div>
      <Link class="bg-orange-500 px-20 py-10 rounded-full my-40" href="#">Join us today</Link>
    </div>
  </section>
  

